ifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Vodka-Tonic-1-1.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch2\u003eFrequently Asked Questions\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdetails id=\"faq-question-1733322755132\"\u003e\u003csummary\u003e\u003ch3\u003eWhat is in a Vodka Tonic?\u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e \u003cp\u003eA Vodka Tonic is a spin off a Gin and Tonic, only made with vodka. The ingredients in a Vodka Tonic are vodka, fresh lime juice and tonic water. It is served with ice in a highball glass. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/details\u003e \u003cdetails id=\"faq-question-1733322762517\"\u003e\u003csummary\u003e\u003ch3\u003eWhat is the difference between a Vodka Soda and a Vodka Tonic?\u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e \u003cp\u003eA Vodka Soda is made with soda water (seltzer or club soda) while a Vodka Tonic is made with sweeter, more flavorful tonic water. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/details\u003e \u003cdetails id=\"faq-question-1733322761811\"\u003e\u003csummary\u003e\u003ch3\u003eIs a Vodka Tonic good? \u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e \u003cp\u003eIf you like a Gin and Tonic or a Vodka Soda, you will most likely love a Vodka Tonic. If you want to add more flavor, try adding extra lime juice or a splash of cranberry juice. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/details\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"960\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/vodka-tonic/?tp_image_id=134070\" data-pin-title=\"Vodka Tonic Recipe\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Vodka-Tonic-1-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Vodka-Tonic-1-2.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Vodka-Tonic-1-2-300x240.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Vodka-Tonic-1-2-1024x819.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Vodka-Tonic-1-2-768x614.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/